    "body": "Hi,\r\nI want to send a hyperlink in text message. I want to do something like this\r\n$w->sendMessage($target, \"Hey WhatsApi <a href='https://github.com/venomous0x/WhatsAPI/issues/666'>Link</a>\");\r\n\r\nBut when I received on Mobile it is a simple text.\r\nHow can I do this.\r\n\r\nThanks",
